---
title: Merative Integrated Care Release Notes
description: 
---

Merative Integrated Care release notes provide brief details on new and updated features, resolved issues, and known issues.

For versions that were released before 1 October 2022, see the Merative Integrated Care [release notes page](https://www.merative.com/support/integrated-care/release-notes/release-notes) on the Merative website.

Release notes for releases after 1 October 2022 are published on this page under the following section.

## Release notes from 1 October 2022

* [Release notes July 2023](/pdf/wcm/MerativeIntegratedCare_ReleaseNotes_July2023.pdf)
* [Release notes June 2023](/pdf/wcm/MerativeIntegratedCare_ReleaseNotes_June2023.pdf)
* [Release notes May 2023](/pdf/wcm/MerativeIntegratedCare_ReleaseNotes_May2023.pdf)
* [Release notes April 2023](/pdf/wcm/MerativeIntegratedCare_ReleaseNotes_April2023.pdf)
* [Release notes March 2023](/pdf/wcm/MerativeIntegratedCare_ReleaseNotes_March2023.pdf)
* [Release notes February 2023](/pdf/wcm/MerativeIntegratedCare_ReleaseNotes_February2023.pdf)
* [Release notes January 2023](/pdf/wcm/MerativeIntegratedCare_ReleaseNotes_January2023.pdf)
* [Release notes November 2022](/pdf/wcm/MerativeIntegratedCare_ReleaseNotes_November22.pdf)
